commentary: Jarvis to Sabbir Rahman, OUT Ervine has plucked out a stunner! This is something! He's leaped one-handed to his left at short midwicket and somehow got his hand under it. Superb. It's a short ball from Jarvis, on a middle and off line. The pull shot is nailed off the middle of the bat and dips on Ervine, but he's got down rapidly and done this with some craft. Despite the speed at which he had to move, he completes the catch nicely with a soft landing and a firm elbow
